        """
        Global Position Covariance Matrix (lat, long, alt, Vn, Ve, Vd).

        time_boot_ms              : Timestamp (UNIX Epoch time or time since system boot). The receiving end can infer timestamp format (since 1.1.1970 or since system boot) by checking for the magnitude of the number. [ms] (type:uint32_t)
