        """
        Pandion Log status

        log_writer_state          : Log Writer current state (type:uint8_t)
        current_log_file          : Current log file (type:uint8_t)
        storage_size_bytes        : Size of storage device (type:uint64_t)
        log_file_bytes_written        : Bytes written to log file (type:uint32_t)
        log_file_max_size_bytes        : Max size of log file in bytes (type:uint32_t)
