        storage_device_failure        : Storage device failure (type:uint8_t)
        filesystem_failure        : Filesystem failure (type:uint8_t)
        log_fifo_high_watermark_kilobytes        : High watermark for log FIFO in kilobytes (type:uint32_t)
        storage_used_bytes        : Number of bytes currently in use on the stroage device (type:uint64_t)

        """
