        heading_target_deg        : Requested Heading, [0, 360 (not inclusive)] (type:float)
        heading_rate_of_change_dps        : (CURRENTLY UNUSED) greater than or equal to 0, 0 = max rate of change (type:float)
        speed_type                : (CURRENTLY ONLY GROUNDSPEED SUPPORTED) See PANDION_MA_SPEED_TYPE, describes whether speed fields are groundspeed or airspeed (type:uint8_t, values:PANDION_MA_SPEED_TYPE)
