        speed_rate_of_change_mps2        : (CURRENTLY UNUSED) greater than or equal to 0, 0 = max rate of change (type:float)
        altitude_target_m         : Requested Altitude (type:float)
        altitude_rate_of_change_mps        : (CURRENTLY UNUSED) greater than or equal to 0, where 0 = max rate of change (type:float)

        """
