        zgyro                     : Angular speed around Z axis [mrad/s] (type:int16_t)
        xmag                      : X Magnetic field [mgauss] (type:int16_t)
        ymag                      : Y Magnetic field [mgauss] (type:int16_t)
        zmag                      : Z Magnetic field [mgauss] (type:int16_t)
